5.7863, 146.2037, 146.8088, 145.8815, 145.714, 144.0113, 145.1932, 146.2786, 147.2162, 146.6091, 146.7278, 149.2821, 148.935, 147.2799, 146.6946, 147.0859, 147.563, 148.6517, 147.7143, 147.7199, 148.0362, 148.1915, 148.0115, 147.2278, 147.3893, 147.857, 147.788, 147.8947, 148.354, 148.1703, 148.4093, 147.9117, 146.8593, 146.6993, 145.491, 144.6803, 145.3069, 145.1407, 146.2599, 145.7058, 145.1635, 146.1414, 145.9246, 145.6931, 145.9668, 145.784, 146.1211, 146.2383, 145.8261, 144.6715, 146.5234, 147.6368, 148.3273, 149.1219, 150.4487, 150.5778, 150.9827, 151.9798, 151.5396, 151.705, 152.0283, 151.9237, 152.1193, 152.2446, 150.682, 150.8841, 151.1473, 152.1584, 152.8944, 154.602, 154.93, 153.3908, 153.4149, 154.9211, 155.8797, 158.7444, 160.4636, 161.2796, 161.3867, 162.5373, 163.5827, 164.4716, 166.1379, 166.0052, 164.523, 163.763, 163.6683, 163.3617, 162.9591, 162.4376, 163.0698, 162.5385, 162.0201, 160.6276, 159.1251, 158.2267, 158.3651, 157.5805, 158.7557, 158.5993, 159.2117, 159.7022, 158.5232, 158.9013, 158.5393, 159.1872, 159.4833, 158.8515, 159.8257, 160.2105, 159.833, 159.9201, 160.9167, 162.2373, 162.5651, 162.744, 163.0568, 163.4716, 163.3444, 161.6716, 162.7833, 163.5345, 163.258, 163.9961, 163.189, 162.9908, 162.9593, 161.7954, 161.8534, 161.7623, 160.1836, 161.0142, 161.1659, 160.4871, 160.4857, 159.5599, 160.8803, 160.4718, 160.756, 160.4702, 160.3185, 161.1917, 160.7107, 160.8621, 162.175, 160.7511, 161.2167, 163.0649, 163.5587, 163.3369, 163.605, 163.5889, 163.8407, 163.7667, 164.3883, 161.8136, 160.1857, 159.9626, 159.9323, 161.2531, 161.2402, 160.4032, 160.838, 160.9998, 161.9176, 162.8989, 162.4448, 162.5451, 162.605, 162.7148, 162.5501, 164.8974, 165.2349, 166.0345, 167.4754, 169.2071, 167.7261, 169.3787, 169.0792, 170.8686, 170.6563, 170.7212, 171.0728, 173.9221, 174.308, 174.0949, 173.2919, 172.9013, 173.4401, 173.3613, 172.3803, 172.143, 171.9107], "summary_html": "<h1>多因子方向打分复合择时信号</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报原文使用6个宏观因子（美国公共债务、央行购金、美元指数、实际利率、CFTC多头持仓、利率期限差）对黄金进行月度方向打分择时。核心逻辑是：每个因子按月度环比变化方向打分 +1/-1，所有因子分数累加得复合分数，超过阈值则入场。</p>\n<p>本复现提取了\"多因子方向打分 -&gt; 复合分数 -&gt; 阈值/连续仓位\"的通用框架，将6个宏观因子替换为商品期货可用的基本面+量价因子（展期收益EMA、基差、席位持仓、持仓量、价格动量、库存），推广到全品种商品期货。策略之所以有效，是因为多个独立维度的方向一致性信号叠加后，形成了类似\"多头共振\"的确认效果，过滤了单因子噪声。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.64</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-14.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.51</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>3.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.82 / 0.25</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.51</td><td>0.13</td><td>0.96</td><td>0.92</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.39</span></td><td>0.43</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.68</span></td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.1</span></td><td>0.17</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.55</span></td><td>1.99</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.5</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>70.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>32.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>每个因子 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">s</span> 上的方向得分：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{score}_{i,s,t} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if } F_{i,s,t} &gt; F_{i,s,t-W} \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if } F_{i,s,t} &lt; F_{i,s,t-W} \\\\ \\text{null} &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">F_i</span> 为第 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 个因子值，<span class=\"math-tex\">W=50</span> 天（约2.5个月）。展期收益使用EMA(252)平滑版本 <code>ryminusema252</code>。库存因子方向取反（库存下降=看多）。</p>\n<p>复合分数（要求至少4个因子有效，过滤低质量观测）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">C_{s,t} = \\sum_{i=1}^{6} \\text{score}_{i,s,t} \\quad (\\text{null 视为 0，要求} \\geq 4 \\text{个因子有效})</div>\n<p>连续仓位信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{s,t} = \\frac{C_{s,t}}{6}</div>\n<p>经过滚动IC gate（min_ic=0.01）过滤弱品种，再做 vol-target 缩放（目标15%年化波动）和15天再平衡。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>Sharpe</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.73, 换手0.78, SM/C亏损大</td><td>5变体(连续/阈值/排名), vol_target+rebalance</td><td>0.73</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>m21偏短, IC gate可过滤弱品种</td><td>加IC gate, 扩展mom_w到42/63, 参数grid</td><td>0.79</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>0.79接近阈值, 尝试参数细化</td><td>vol/hold参数网格, 结果回退</td><td>0.73</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>回到R2最优配置</td><td>保持R2 spec</td><td>0.79</td></tr><tr><td>R5</td><td>数据更新后降至0.76; composite4(n_valid&gt;=4)比基线好</td><td>composite4+IC gate 0.01+参数网格</td><td>0.76</td></tr><tr><td>R6</td><td>尝试EMA平滑展期收益(ryminusema252)</td><td>EMA-ry+composite4+m50+hold15</td><td><strong>0.86</strong></td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>R1-&gt;R2: 动量窗口21-&gt;42天（更符合中长期），IC gate过滤弱品种，+0.06</li>\n<li>R5: 引入composite4 (n_valid&gt;=4)质量筛选，过滤低质量观测点，+0.02</li>\n<li>R6: 使用EMA(252)平滑的展期收益替代原始ry，降低了ry因子的高频噪声；将动量窗口从42延长到50天；再平衡从21天缩短到15天提高响应速度。三项改进叠加将Sharpe从0.76推至0.86</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（中期信号）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（~58个），IC gate自动过滤弱品种</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原文使用外部宏观数据(美债/央行购金/DXY等)，本复现用商品基本面因子替代，信号来源完全不同\n<p>- 截面IC弱(0.009)，策略主要靠时序维度的方向打分 - 基本面字段(ryminusema252/basis/memberdiff20/inventory_21)有20-45%缺失，限制了部分品种信号覆盖 - 半样本前强后弱(1.32 vs 0.69)，后半仍正但需关注衰减 - 与因子库xinye展期收益因子相关性0.42，尚在阈值内但需注意</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_W</code></td><td><code>50</code></td><td>direction momentum window (days)</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>15</code></td><td>rebalance hold</td></tr><tr><td><code>N_VALID_MIN</code></td><td><code>4</code></td><td>require &gt;=4 of 6 factors valid</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.14s</li>\n</ul>"}